parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Sudden Loss of Power and Warning Light Illumination
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden loss of power and illumination of warning lights can cause a loss of vehicle control, increasing the risk of accidents, and potentially leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power while driving
all warning lights start flashing
the vehicle shuts down without warning
the vehicle stalls or dies while driving
the vehicle experiences a sudden loss of acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexpected deployment of airbags can cause physical harm, including head trauma, loss of consciousness, and dental injuries, and may lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Airbag deploys without warning
airbag deploys when the vehicle is not in motion
airbag deploys when the door is opened
airbag deploys when the key fob is used to unlock the vehicle
driver is struck by the airbag
driver experiences head trauma
driver loses consciousness
driver suffers dental injuries.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A chafed airbag wire can cause the airbag to deploy unexpectedly, leading to physical harm and potential accidents.
symptoms: Airbag deploys without warning
airbag deploys when the vehicle is not in motion
airbag wire is damaged
airbag wire is chafed
airbag system malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat support bracket can cause the seat to shift suddenly, leading to unintended steering inputs, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The seat shifts suddenly
the seat tilts to one side
the driver experiences unintended steering inputs
the seat attachment breaks at the left or right rear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to slip or hesitate when shifting gears, leading to loss of control, accidents, or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or slips when shifting gears
the transmission slips or hesitates when accelerating
the transmission makes unusual noises or vibrations
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear
the vehicle stalls or loses power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the throttle control system can cause the vehicle to lose power during acceleration, leading to a loss of control and increased risk of accidents, especially in heavy traffic.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power during acceleration
the vehicle stalls
the cruise control malfunctions
the throttle pedal feels unresponsive or sluggish.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the throttle body assembly can cause the vehicle to lose power during acceleration, leading to a loss of control and increased risk of accidents, especially in heavy traffic.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power during acceleration
the vehicle stalls
the cruise control malfunctions
the throttle pedal feels unresponsive or sluggish.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause accessories such as the cigarette lighter to malfunction, leading to inconvenience and potential safety risks.
symptoms: The cigarette lighter is inoperable
a blown fuse is detected.
